headline: Revisiting EMCOR Group (EME) Valuation After 11% Pullback and Strong Year-to-Date Gains
summary: EMCOR Group (EME) has quietly caught some attention among investors lately, especially as its stock has retraced over the past month, dipping 11% from recent highs.
